              "translation": "In his absence she could not control her passion and invited a person to live with her in the house.(3)",
              "additional_information": {}
            }
          },
          "Punjabi": {
            "Dr. Rattan Singh Jaggi": {
              "translation": "ਆਪਣੇ ਘਰ ਵਿਚ ਇਕ ਪੁਰਸ਼ ਬੁਲਾ ਕੇ ਰਖ ਲਿਆ ॥੩॥",
              "additional_information": {}
            }
          }
        }
